    "App Store 应用不支持迁移，因为迁移后将无法通过 App Store 更新。\\n\\n如需强制迁移，请在设置中启用相应选项。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "App Store apps cannot be migrated because they won't be updatable via App Store after migration.\\n\\nTo force migration, enable the option in Settings."
          }
        },
        "br": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "⠠⠁⠏⠏ ⠠⠎⠞⠕⠗⠑ ⠁⠏⠏⠎ ⠉⠁⠝⠝⠕⠞ ⠃⠑ ⠍⠊⠛⠗⠁⠞⠑⠙ ⠃⠑⠉⠁⠥⠎⠑ ⠞⠓⠑⠽ ⠺⠕⠝⠄⠞ ⠃⠑ ⠥⠏⠙⠁⠞⠁⠃⠇⠑ ⠧⠊⠁ ⠠⠁⠏⠏ ⠠⠎⠞⠕⠗⠑ ⠁⠋⠞⠑⠗ ⠍⠊⠛⠗⠁⠞⠊⠕⠝⠲\\⠝\\⠝⠠⠞⠕ ⠋⠕⠗⠉⠑ ⠍⠊⠛⠗⠁⠞⠊⠕⠝⠂ ⠑⠝⠁⠃⠇⠑ ⠞⠓⠑ ⠕⠏⠞⠊⠕⠝ ⠊⠝ ⠠⠎⠑⠞⠞⠊⠝⠛⠎⠲"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "App Store apps cannot be migrated because they won't be updatable via App Store after migration.\\n\\nTo force migration, enable the option in Settings."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "App Store apps cannot be migrated because they won't be updatable via App Store after migration.\\n\\nTo force migration, enable the option in Settings."
          }
        },
        "eo": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "App Store apps cannot be migrated because they won't be updatable via App Store after migration.\\n\\nTo force migration, enable the option in Settings."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "App Store apps cannot be migrated because they won't be updatable via App Store after migration.\\n\\nTo force migration, enable the option in Settings."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
